    "p": "See The First Reactor, another booklet in this series. See Nuclear Reactors and Nuclear Power Plants, companion booklets in this series. See Breeder Reactors, another booklet in this series. See Thorium&mdash;and the Third Fuel, another booklet in this series. See Controlled Nuclear Fusion, another booklet in this series. ",
    "len": 50
  },
